    "Tenemos = we have",
    "Tienen = they have / you plural have",
    "Tener expressions: use tener + noun for feelings/states",
    "Tener hambre = to be hungry (literally 'to have hunger')",
    "Tener sed = to be thirsty",
    "Tener frío = to be cold",
    "Tener calor = to be hot"
